            "title": "泰德醫藥開市較招股價低1%  現跌近4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泰德醫藥(03880)今日首掛，開報30.3元，較招股價30.6元低1%，每手100股計，不計手續費，每手蝕30元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"泰德醫藥招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/03880-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"泰德醫藥招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/03880-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">泰德醫藥招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">現跌3.76%，報29.45元，一手蝕115元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股公開發售獲超額認購300.15倍，一手中籤率50%，認購200手穩中一手，以招股價28.40元至30.60元範圍之上限定價。</p>\n</div>",
