            "title": "IFBH高開近58%   每手賺3220元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">IFBH(06603)首掛，開報43.9元，較招股價27.8元高57.9%。為今早三新股中表現最好。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"IFBH今首掛，管理層致詞。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250630_FI_IFBH_BP_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"IFBH今首掛，管理層致詞。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250630_FI_IFBH_BP_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">IFBH今首掛，管理層致詞。</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">不計手續費，每手200股賺3220元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">IFBH上限價，超額認購2681.35倍，共23.6萬人申請，一手中籤率10%。暗盤升60%</p>\n</div>",
