        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段變動不大 恒指微跌9點報24274點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段變動不大，恒生指數開市報24274點，跌9點或0.04%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5351點，升10點或0.2%；國企指數以8766點開市，升3點或0.05%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股於競價時段，阿里巴巴(09988)開報111.5元，跌0.54%；騰訊(00700)開報509元，跌0.78%；美團(03690)開報128.6元，跌0.62%；京東(09618)開報130.9元，升0.46。滙控(00005)開報95元，暫時無升跌；友邦(01299)開報71.25元，跌0.49%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米雷軍官方微博\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250521_FI_source-web_01810-YU7-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米雷軍官方微博\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250521_FI_source-web_01810-YU7-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米雷軍官方微博</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">有擬小米(01810)剛推售的小米YU7汽車出現黃牛炒作，另有報道指YU7賽道測試剎車片起火，小米對後者回應指，是因為未進行散熱圈的極端情況下直接駐車而道致。該股今早開市持續向好，報59.5元，升0.93%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15051133-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e8%ae%8a%e5%8b%95%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%a7-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%be%ae%e8%b7%8c9%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b124274%e9%bb%9e",
